N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 561.7 - Amendments and revisions

State Regulations

This Part shall be subject to amendment or revision. Any
amendments or revisions thereof shall be filed as required within 30 days after
adoption by the Board of Trustees of the State University of New
